item.title: RKLB
item.description: score:61 Chances: Rocket Lab has successfully launched its 44th Electron rocket and deployed an orbital debris inspection satellite, showcasing its consistent capability in providing launch services and space systems. The FAA approval for reentry of Varda Space Industries’ in-space manufacturing capsule demonstrates Rocket Lab’s technical and regulatory competence in managing complex in-space maneuvers.
